## Performance

MongoKitten is faster than other MongoDB drivers.

Driver | Execution time
-------|----------------
MongoKitten 4 | 525ms
Java (post JIT optimizations) | 585ms
C                        | 605ms
Ruby                     | 1200ms
Java (pre JIT optimizations) | 1205ms

